<main class="page-users">

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">âœ¦ Your life, your list</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">What do you want<br>to <em>do</em> before you die?</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Add yourself below, then start building your bucket list. Track dreams, mark wins, live boldly.</p>
